g.text: Matthew 1-7: Genealogy and Early Ministry Journey of Jesus

path.id: Bethlehem: Visit of the Magi (Ch 2)-to-Egypt: Flight to Egypt (Ch 2)
Egypt: Flight to Egypt (Ch 2)-to-Nazareth: Return & Hidden Life (Ch 2)
Nazareth: Return & Hidden Life (Ch 2)-to-Jordan River: John the Baptist (Ch 3)
Jordan River: John the Baptist (Ch 3)-to-Judean Desert: Temptation (Ch 4)
Judean Desert: Temptation (Ch 4)-to-Galilee: Start of Public Ministry (Ch 4)
Beatitudes & Moral Teaching (Ch 5)-to-Piety & Trust in God (Ch 6)
Piety & Trust in God (Ch 6)-to-Judgment, Prayer & Wisdom (Ch 7)
Galilee: Start of Public Ministry (Ch 4)-to-Sermon on the Mount (Matthew 5-7)
